{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"gmain","type":"group","x":-80,"y":0,"width":4200,"height":920},
		{"id":"gaux","type":"group","x":-80,"y":1020,"width":3740,"height":560},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# gstack 工作流全景图\n虚拟工程团队 · 运行时基础设施 · Think -> Plan -> Build -> Review -> Test -> Ship -> Reflect","x":700,"y":-640,"width":1220,"height":160},
		{"id":"vision","type":"text","text":"## 核心心智模型\n\n**gstack 不是单个技能包，而是 Claude Code 上的软件工厂。**\n\n它把一个产品交付过程拆成多个专家角色：YC 合伙人、CEO、工程经理、设计师、QA、安全、发布工程师、SRE。\n\n关键词：完整性、真实浏览器、审查流水线、持续学习。","x":-40,"y":-420,"width":420,"height":250},
		{"id":"runtime","type":"text","text":"## 运行时层\n\n每个技能前面都有厚重 preamble：\n- 自动更新检查\n- repo mode / branch / session 识别\n- telemetry / analytics\n- project learnings 注入\n- skill routing 提示\n- gbrain context queries\n\n这让技能像应用，不只是提示词。","x":440,"y":-420,"width":420,"height":250},
		{"id":"ethos","type":"text","text":"## 建造哲学\n\n来自 `ETHOS.md` 的三条底层偏好：\n- Boil the Lake：AI 让完整实现的边际成本变低\n- Search Before Building：先查已有方案\n- User Sovereignty：模型推荐，用户决定\n\n所以 gstack 倾向扩大审查和验证，而不是最小仪式。","x":920,"y":-420,"width":420,"height":250},
		{"id":"sources","type":"text","text":"## 拆解依据\n\n来源仓库：[garrytan/gstack](https://github.com/garrytan/gstack)\n\n重点读取：\n- `README.md`：The sprint 与技能总表\n- `ETHOS.md`：Boil the Lake / Search / User Sovereignty\n- `ARCHITECTURE.md`：浏览器 daemon 与安全模型\n- `SKILL.md` 与各 `SKILL.md.tmpl`：preamble、routing、具体流程\n- `docs/OPENCLAW.md`：跨 agent 分层派发","x":1400,"y":-420,"width":860,"height":250},
		{"id":"setup","type":"text","text":"## 0. 安装与路由\n\n`./setup` 安装到多个 host：Claude Code、Codex、Cursor、OpenCode 等。\n\nTeam mode 会把 gstack 作为 repo 约定写入 `CLAUDE.md`。\n\n**作用**：让 agent 在看到任务时能主动建议或调用对应 slash command。","x":-40,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"ceo","type":"text","text":"### CEO Review\n`/plan-ceo-review`\n\n重审问题和野心：\n- Expansion\n- Selective expansion\n- Hold scope\n- Reduction\n\n看这个计划是否值得做、是否太小、是否错过 10-star product。","x":1060,"y":60,"width":260,"height":270},
		{"id":"eng","type":"text","text":"### Eng Review\n`/plan-eng-review`\n\n工程经理模式：\n- 架构图\n- 数据流\n- 状态机\n- 错误路径\n- 测试矩阵\n\n把隐性工程假设变成可审查的计划。","x":1380,"y":60,"width":260,"height":270},
		{"id":"think","type":"text","text":"## 1. Think\n### `/office-hours`\n\n两种模式：\n- Startup / intrapreneurship：六个 YC forcing questions\n- Builder：设计思考式 brainstorm\n\n**产物**：design doc。\n\n**硬门禁**：此阶段不写代码，只把问题和 wedge 讲清楚。","x":320,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"design","type":"text","text":"### Design Review\n`/plan-design-review`\n\n计划阶段的设计审查：\n- 设计维度打分\n- AI slop 检测\n- 具体到界面选择\n- 通过 AskUserQuestion 保留 taste 判断\n\n后续可接 `/design-review` 做真实页面修复。","x":1060,"y":390,"width":260,"height":270},
		{"id":"dx","type":"text","text":"### DX Review\n`/plan-devex-review`\n\n面向开发者产品：\n- persona\n- time to hello world\n- 魔法时刻\n- 摩擦点追踪\n\n对应 live audit 是 `/devex-review`。","x":1380,"y":390,"width":260,"height":270},
		{"id":"build","type":"text","text":"## 3. Build\n\ngstack 本身不把写代码封装成一个单独技能，而是让 Claude Code 执行被 review 过的计划。\n\n关键约束：\n- 先理解项目指令\n- 遵守计划与 decision log\n- 遇到 taste / 用户方向变更时回问\n- 完整实现 blast radius 内的问题","x":1720,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"review","type":"text","text":"## 4. Review\n\n核心技能：\n- `/review`：staff engineer 找生产级 bug\n- `/codex`：跨模型 second opinion\n- `/cso`：OWASP + STRIDE 安全审计\n\n倾向：自动修明显问题，复杂或方向性问题交给用户。","x":2080,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"test","type":"text","text":"## 5. Test\n\n真实反馈回路：\n- `/qa`：浏览器里点真实流程，找 bug 并修复\n- `/qa-only`：只报告，不改代码\n- `/benchmark`：性能基线与回归\n- `/browse`：给 agent 眼睛、截图和交互能力\n\n这是 gstack 区别于纯 prompt 包的关键。","x":2440,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"ship","type":"text","text":"## 6. Ship\n\n发布工程师链路：\n- `/ship`：同步 main、跑测试、补测试框架、push、开 PR\n- `/setup-deploy`：一次性配置部署信息\n- `/document-release`：把文档更新到刚发布的行为\n\n目标是把交付末端也流程化。","x":2800,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"deploy","type":"text","text":"## 7. Deploy\n\n生产闭环：\n- `/land-and-deploy`：合并 PR，等待 CI / deploy，验证生产健康\n- `/canary`：部署后持续监控页面、console、性能、截图\n\n从 approved PR 到 production verified。","x":3160,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"reflect","type":"text","text":"## 8. Reflect\n\n长期复利：\n- `/retro`：周度工程复盘\n- `/learn`：查看、搜索、修剪 project learnings\n- `/context-save` / `/context-restore`：保存和恢复会话上下文\n- `/skillify`：把成功套路固化为新技能\n\n每次交付都反哺下一次。","x":3520,"y":80,"width":300,"height":300},
		{"id":"browser","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 A：浏览器系统\n\n`/browse` 背后是长驻 Chromium daemon：\n- 首次启动，后续命令 100-200ms\n- cookies / tabs / localStorage 持久\n- 本地 HTTP + CDP\n- 截图、表单、dialog、responsive、network、console\n\n`/pair-agent` 还能把浏览器 tab 共享给远程 agent。","x":-40,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"safety","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 B：安全护栏\n\n- `/careful`：危险命令前提醒\n- `/freeze`：限制编辑目录\n- `/guard`：careful + freeze\n- `/unfreeze`：解除边界\n- `/cso`：安全审计\n\n`/investigate` 还会在确认根因后锁定 debug scope，防止修 bug 时扩散。","x":440,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"debug","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 C：调查式调试\n\n`/investigate` 的铁律：\n**NO FIXES WITHOUT ROOT CAUSE**。\n\n流程：\n1. 收集症状和近期变更\n2. 复现并提出可验证假设\n3. 用日志/断言验证\n4. 锁定 scope 后修根因\n5. 写 regression test\n6. fresh verification + report","x":920,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"designloop","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 D：设计生产线\n\n- `/design-consultation`：从零建立设计系统\n- `/design-shotgun`：生成 4-6 个方向，让用户选 taste\n- `/design-html`：把 mockup 变成可运行 HTML\n- `/design-review`：真实页面审查与修复\n\n这是产品 taste 被显式化、记忆化的子系统。","x":1400,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"memory","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 E：记忆与上下文\n\ngstack 会维护：\n- `~/.gstack/projects/{slug}/learnings.jsonl`\n- timeline / analytics\n- builder profile / taste profile\n- gbrain repo indexing 与 context queries\n\n技能启动时读取相关学习，减少重复踩坑。","x":1880,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"openclaw","type":"text","text":"## 横切能力 F：跨 agent 适配\n\ngstack 支持多 host 安装，并为 OpenClaw 定义分层派发：\n- Simple：不用 gstack\n- Medium：gstack-lite planning discipline\n- Heavy：指定 `/skill`\n- Full：`/autoplan` -> implement -> `/ship`\n- Plan：只产出 reviewed plan\n\n提示词就是桥。","x":2360,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"risk","type":"text","text":"## 代价与风险\n\n优势：端到端、真实反馈、角色齐全、能积累记忆。\n\n代价：\n- 流程重，适合大任务多于小修小补\n- opinionated，默认偏完整实现\n- 运行时复杂度高：daemon、配置、telemetry、learn files\n- 需要用户能判断何时接受扩大 scope","x":2840,"y":1100,"width":420,"height":370},
		{"id":"plan","type":"text","text":"## 2. Plan\n### `/autoplan`\n\n自动跑完整 review gauntlet：\nCEO -> Design -> Eng -> DX。\n\n用 6 条原则自动回答中间问题：\n- completeness\n- boil lakes\n- pragmatic\n- DRY\n- explicit\n- action bias\n\nTaste / User Challenge 留给用户最终拍板。","x":650,"y":80,"width":320,"height":300}
	],
